पाबूजी राजस्थान में ऊँटो के देवता, लक्ष्मण के अवतार एवं प्लेग रक्षक देवता के नाम से जाने जाते है जो देवल चारणी की गायो को अपने बहनोई से छुड़वाते हुए वीरगति को प्राप्त हो जाते है। पाबू जी के पावड़े माठ वाद्य यंत्र के साथ थोरी जाती के लोगो द्वारा गाये जाने वाले पाबूजी के गाथा गीत है और पाबूजी की फड़ का वाचन नायक/रेबारी जाती के भोपों द्वारा रावणहत्था वाद्य यंत्र के साथ करते है।

snippet.textDisplay:
The actual story is in fact about the day Pabuji was getting ready to approach towards Amarkot but the mare Pabuji had, it wasn’t a skilled one. Maa Deval’s mare was very skilled in all aspects, Pabuji requested Maa Deval to lend that mare to him for some time, till he returns from Amarkot. 
Maa Deval’s mare used to protect her domesticated cows, so she agreed to lend Pabuji her mare only when he made a promise to return at once if her cows were in danger. 
And so it happened, Maa Deval’s cows were in danger, so she got infuriated and took her ‘vikraal roop’ as she was a Charani Sagat, when Pabuji learnt of this he immediately left his own wedding and fought against the perpetrators, he then gained martyrdom, his wife then became a Sati.
